      "title": "The service will be suspended from Monday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The All Sri Lanka School Children Transport Association has warned that if the fuel issue is not resolved by tomorrow (28), they will withdraw from the service from Monday.",
        "The association has demanded that fuel should be supplied to school vehicles through Sri Lanka Transport Board depots."
      ],
